headline: HEINZ and Herschel Supply Debut New Luggage Collection Packing Both Flavor and Style
summary: PITTSBURGH, CHICAGO, & VANCOUVER, British Columbia, November 04, 2025--Today, HEINZ, the global leader in condiments, is partnering with global lifestyle brand, Herschel Supply, to announce a first-ever collaboration uniting flavor and style.
